me.leoko.advancedgui.manager

Class GuiWallManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • me.leoko.advancedgui.manager.GuiWallManager

  • public class GuiWallManager
extends Object
    The GuiWallManager manages available GuiWallInstances and renders their standby interaction.

    • Field Summary

      static int SIGHT_RADIUS

      • registerInstance

        public void registerInstance(GuiWallInstance instance,
                             boolean save)
        Registers a new wall instance allowing players to interact with it and to see the standby screen. When save is set to true then the instance will be saved to file and automatically be loaded from now on.
        Parameters:
        instance - the instance
        save - whether to save the instance

      • unregisterInstance

        public void unregisterInstance(GuiWallInstance instance,
                               boolean delete)
        Unregisters the instance reverting the registerInstance(GuiWallInstance, boolean) method.
        Parameters:
        instance - the instance
        delete - whether to delete the instance from file
